<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>⦗١٤٧⦘<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>١٦٦٩٥ - عَنْ إِسْمَاعِيلَ، عَنِ ابْنِ عَوْنٍ، عَنِ الْقَاسِمِ،<span class="c5"> وَعُمَرِ بْنِ عَبْدِ الْعَزِيزِ قَالَا:</span> <span class="c2">«أَوْلَادُ الْمُدَبَّرَةِ بِمَنْزِلَةِ أُمِّهِمْ»</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>